  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DON'T GET CAUGHT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/2bbe1a938a56a6c486f53236ca43f19a.poster.avif?t=1709880601\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/2bbe1a938a56a6c486f53236ca43f19a.webm?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/2bbe1a938a56a6c486f53236ca43f19a.mp4?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The demon goes hunting and will chase you, getting progressively more difficult as the game goes on. Use a combination of sprinting, walking, and resting to escape it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/4439fc069ad6a57ee320e0275e668c19.poster.avif?t=1709880601\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/4439fc069ad6a57ee320e0275e668c19.webm?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/4439fc069ad6a57ee320e0275e668c19.mp4?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Uncover helpful hints and character memories through notes and playable flashbacks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEAL IT AWAY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/8ce841f64b7581d049f698e7962fcb70.poster.avif?t=1709880601\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/8ce841f64b7581d049f698e7962fcb70.webm?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/8ce841f64b7581d049f698e7962fcb70.mp4?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your collected candles to perform a ritual and seal the demon away to survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AUDIO AND SOUND</h2>CANDLES has a carefully crafted original soundtrack with an emphasis on silence and tension. All sound effects in the game are original and compose a rich and unique sound palette to enhance the experience.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DON'T GET CAUGHT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/2bbe1a938a56a6c486f53236ca43f19a.poster.avif?t=1709880601\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/2bbe1a938a56a6c486f53236ca43f19a.webm?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/2bbe1a938a56a6c486f53236ca43f19a.mp4?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The demon goes hunting and will chase you, getting progressively more difficult as the game goes on. Use a combination of sprinting, walking, and resting to escape it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/4439fc069ad6a57ee320e0275e668c19.poster.avif?t=1709880601\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/4439fc069ad6a57ee320e0275e668c19.webm?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/4439fc069ad6a57ee320e0275e668c19.mp4?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Uncover helpful hints and character memories through notes and playable flashbacks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEAL IT AWAY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/8ce841f64b7581d049f698e7962fcb70.poster.avif?t=1709880601\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/8ce841f64b7581d049f698e7962fcb70.webm?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525560/extras/8ce841f64b7581d049f698e7962fcb70.mp4?t=1709880601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your collected candles to perform a ritual and seal the demon away to survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AUDIO AND SOUND</h2>CANDLES has a carefully crafted original soundtrack with an emphasis on silence and tension. All sound effects in the game are original and compose a rich and unique sound palette to enhance the experience.",
